### Button Components

#### Primary Button
- Background: Primary Blue (#2B579A)
- Text: White
- Border Radius: 6px
- Padding: 12px 24px
- Font: Button Primary
- Hover: Darken background by 10%
- Variants: Default, Hover, Disabled, Loading

#### Secondary Button
- Background: White
- Border: 1px solid Primary Blue
- Text: Primary Blue
- Border Radius: 6px
- Padding: 12px 24px
- Font: Button Secondary
- Hover: Light blue background

#### Icon Button
- Size: 40x40px
- Background: Transparent
- Icon: 20x20px centered
- Border Radius: 6px
- Hover: Light gray background

### Card Components

#### Stats Card
- Size: 320x120px
- Background: White
- Border Radius: 8px
- Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- Padding: 24px
- Structure:
  - Icon (24x24px) + Title (H3)
  - Value (48px Bold Primary Blue)
  - Trend (Small text with arrow)

#### Content Card
- Background: White
- Border Radius: 8px
- Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- Padding: 24px
- Header: H3 + optional action button
- Content: Flexible height

