- 8px: sm
- 12px: md
- 16px: lg
- 24px: xl
- 32px: 2xl
- 48px: 3xl
- 64px: 4xl

### Breakpoints
- Mobile: < 768px
- Tablet: 768px - 1199px
- Desktop: â‰¥ 1200px

### Grid System
- Container: Max 1440px
- Columns: 12 column grid
- Gutter: 32px
